NAME
    ips.pl - Patches a file with records provided from IPS patches.

SYNOPSIS
            ips.pl file1 patch1.ips ... file2 patch2.ips ...

DESCRIPTION
    ips.pl is a reimplementation of a Perl script found in the wild
    (<http://www.zophar.net/utilities/patchutil/ips-pl.html>) which will
    apply patches in the IPS format to the file specified. The IPS file
    format can be found at <http://zerosoft.zophar.net/ips.php>. It supports
    RLE (Run Length Encoded) IPS patches as well.

  Flags
    *   ips.pl --merge=newpatch.ips patch1.ips patch2.ips

        Merges multiple IPS patches into one IPS patch.

HOMEPAGE
    <http://github.com/chinesefood/ips.pl/tree/master>

